<s> Favored ventures include media , telecommunications and retailing . </s>
<s> Most popular acquisition method : the leveraged buy-out . </s>
<s> Family-owned firms that need cash to grow are attractive , says John Turner of Matuschka Gruppe , Munich . </s>
